document_data.name: Morgan's Warehouse
document_data.mainbody: '''Morgan's Warehouse''' was a warehouse in the [[Skullport/Lower Port|Lower Port]] of [[Skullport]] in the late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Structure: The warehouse was a two-story structure in fair condition.
document_data.Description: The warehouse was known as one of the most secure and reliable depots in Skullport. Goods passing through Morgan's Warehouse were well-protected, making it a trusted establishment for merchants seeking dependable storage.
